comment._content: The Tug 'Gamecock' was launched 06/01/1886 - see full details - SMH 11/01/1886 p.6 - trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/28359746 Still working in 1950 (!) - trove.nla.gov.au/ndp/del/article/18140239 I wonder what the rust-bucket barque (?) in the background is?

comment._content: [http://www.flickr.com/photos/beachcomberaustralia] Yes I wonder what that vessel is, it looks as though it is in need of some R&R. Upon blowing up the image no name is visible, but there are a few detailed finger prints, lovely to have such a personal mark of the photographer :)
